{"tid":1824553,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【幫手頂置】(行動PO) 新春一連四日特別大行動","createTime":"2020-01-14T14:02:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T14:02:39.000Z","uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0cad4a082bf5acaf1cf83aedac533c1d9fae5a09","tid":1824553,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T14:02:39.000Z","msg":"大家好 又係我地<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">SUCK Channel</span></strong><br />\n農歷新年  當然又係大家行動既時候啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n農歷新年我地發起  <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一年在計在於  SUCK !  一連4日大行動 </span></span></strong><br />\n因為今次行動係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>一連四日</strong></span> 所以篇文比較長  <br />\n希望大家可以<span style=\"color: red;\">睇晒佢</span>慢慢消化   <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n文宣首先放晒係度<br />\n大家請慢慢向下睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SXMqKZh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSXMqKZh.jpg&h=4e15091e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m9D40ts.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm9D40ts.png&h=df5d96f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ojZLKU5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FojZLKU5.jpg&h=22f7af4d&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MZCdTOr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMZCdTOr.png&h=15e49688&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">新春 年三十晚  搶頭柱香!</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SXMqKZh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSXMqKZh.jpg&h=4e15091e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n首先 新春 年三十晚 點少到搶頭香活動<br />\n無錯 我地<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要每一份力量</span></span></strong>都用到盡<br />\n連<span style=\"color: red;\">神</span>既力量都要用埋  <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為呢個香港上番柱頭香許願  <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n許個<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求缺一不可</span></span>既願望 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為新一年既開始打份基礎<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TSOTTQz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTSOTTQz.jpg&h=bd8fd399&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o3AvbCX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo3AvbCX.jpg&h=3cdb6e35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而且<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">每年搶頭香都有CCTVB既 LIVE</span></strong></span><br />\n到時<span style=\"color: orange;\">舉個牌 叫個口號</span>都係個唔錯既選擇<br />\n<br />\n另外每年黃夏蕙BB都會係<span style=\"color: red;\">搶頭香活動</span>出現<br />\n黃夏蕙BB每年都有精美生肖造型打份<br />\n去野生捕獲一下支持一下黃夏蕙BB<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n稍後#2會為大家詳細介紹一下黃夏蕙BB呢位黃到爆既藝人<br />\n黃夏蕙BB今年其實歲數都已經好大 <br />\n但依然有<span style=\"color: red;\">為反送中運動出力</span>亦被唔少人批判<br />\n係本地少數藝人願意為運動發聲發力之一<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">年初一 大行動  國泰航空新春匯演</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m9D40ts.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm9D40ts.png&h=df5d96f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本年度由於十九正苦應該9成9都唔會放煙花<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n花車巡遊亦取消左  <br />\n改為係西九同<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: teal;\">奶共因航</span></strong></span>舉行呢個新春匯演<br />\n呢個匯演<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大白象工程</span></strong>洗左足足<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">4800萬 只係4日 </span></span>   <br />\n即係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">平均搞一日洗1200萬</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正苦咁隆重既&quot;<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">活動</span></span></strong>&quot;  <br />\n作為香港人 點可以唔&quot;<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">支持</span></strong></span>&quot;呀? <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但現時香港飽受<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">中國肺炎</span></strong>侵襲  <br />\n而又係西九舉行<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">高密度人口活動</span></span></strong><br />\n到時一個唔小心<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">係西九爆發中國肺炎</span></span></strong>咁就唔好啦...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n於是我地為防<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">中國肺炎係本港爆發</span></span></strong><br />\n誠邀大家係西九文化區當日現場<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>派發口罩</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但如果大家真係咁不幸 <br />\n當日現場&quot;<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">感染</span></span>&quot;左<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">中國肺炎</span></strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n戴住口罩&quot;<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">咳</span></strong></span>&quot;兩下都在所難免  <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外我地可預期當日會有人參加完&quot;<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">武漢旅行團</span></span></strong>&quot;番黎之後去左西九玩<br />\n心口如果仲貼住&quot;<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">武漢旅行團</span></span></strong>&quot;就唔係咁好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時有一大班&quot;<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">武漢旅行團</span></span></strong>&quot;戴住口罩係咁<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">咳</span></strong> <br />\n嚇到班<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>港豬 蝗民</strong></span> 雞飛狗走 就唔係咁好啦.... <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">年初二   車公大仙祈福活動</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ojZLKU5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FojZLKU5.jpg&h=22f7af4d&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n講到搶頭柱香  又點少得轉風車同求籤<br />\n<br />\n每年<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">CCTVB同正苦都會派膠棺</span></span>為香港祈福<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然唔知祈到咩福  <br />\n但為左呢個香港 <br />\n作為一個良好市民當然要現身支持 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n19年仲有<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">葉小姐</span></strong></span>親臨沙田車公廟出席香港求籤活動<br />\n如果今年抽到<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>下下籤</strong></span>都真係幾..&quot;<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>大吉利是</strong></span>&quot;  <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於點解去車公廟同黃大仙廟<br />\n為香港同自己轉一下風車 <br />\n趕走衰氣既同時又可以為香港祈福同出一分力<br />\n無成本既野 何樂而不為?<br />\n而且呢D每年<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">只得一次機會</span></strong>同時<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">CCTVB又會公開直播</span></strong>既難得場面  <br />\n點可以放過呀..<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一<br />\n<br />\n年初三  <span style=\"color: red;\">赤口</span>  咳 the SHOP <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MZCdTOr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMZCdTOr.png&h=15e49688&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n年初三<span style=\"color: red;\">赤口</span>不宜拜年大家都知  <br />\n一陣嘈交就唔係咁好啦<br />\n所以年初三就不如出街SHOPPING啦<br />\n<br />\n頭先都提到 年初一可能會有 &quot;<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">武漢旅行團</span></span></strong>&quot; 既出現<br />\n如果大家係SHOPPING既途中遇到  <br />\n記得戴番個<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">醫科口罩</span>呀...<br />\n一陣&quot;<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">感染</span></span>&quot;呢隻新型&quot;<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">冠狀病毒</span></strong></span>&quot; 係無&quot;<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">抗體</span></span></strong>&quot; 架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地係呢度都可以預想到感染得&quot;<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">中國肺炎</span></strong></span>&quot;既人都有以下特徵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. 講蝗語</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2. 戴口罩</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">3. 係咁咳</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n你知尖咀一帶新年幾多人架啦<br />\n一陣試衫又見到 &quot;<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">武漢旅行團</span></strong></span>&quot;<br />\n睇名牌又見到 &quot;<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">武漢旅行團</span></strong></span>&quot;<br />\n食飯又見到  &quot;<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">武漢旅行團</span></strong></span>&quot;<br />\n連行出街都見到  &quot;<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">武漢旅行團</span></strong></span>&quot;<br />\n都咪話你唔驚.... <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一<br />\n<br />\n新年 點少得<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">派利是</span></strong></span>呀!<br />\n請緊記 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">SUCK利是 </span></strong></span>既原則<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xvgKf2j.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxvgKf2j.png&h=dfb289d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">就係向藍說不</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一<br />\n<br />\n最後  請別遺忘  有一眾手足唔可以同屋企人一齊食團年飯<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JtjLKVJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJtjLKVJ.jpg&h=7d059a6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我地必須背負佢地 繼續前行<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人 唔可以輸</span></span></strong>"}]}